title: Comprehensive ST Series USB Cable 2.0 A to B Cable 25 FT
description: Comprehensive: The Cables the Pros Have Trusted Since 1974! For nearly 40 years, Comprehensive cables have been the Pro A/V industry standard for connectivity performance, reliability and value. That's why millions of Comprehensive cables and connectivity products are in use at stadiums, broadcast and recording studios, stages, boardrooms, classrooms, and now living rooms. USB Cables are commonly used to connect computers and peripherals such as printers, scanners, cameras, keyboards, mice and other digital devices. Comprehensive USB cables provide digital signal transmission rates of up to 480Mbps. These cables are constructed of premium shielded twisted pair construction for superior signal transfer and rejection of interference that can effect poorly made cables. Comprehensive USB 2.0 cables are backwards compatible for USB 1.0 and 1.1. RoHS Compliant. Lifetime Warranty.Features include: -USB 2.0 Type A Male to Type B Male -Transfer rates up to 480Mbps -Premium shielded twisted pair construction-Plug and play functionality for printers, scanners, keyboards and other digital devices -PC and Mac compatible-Compatible with USB specifications 1.0, 1.1, and 2.0-Molded Strain Relief-RoHS Compliant-Lifetime Warranty. Cable Construction includes:-Connector Type 1: USB A Male -Connector Type 1: USB B Male -Bandwidth or Speed: Supports Hi-Speed, 480 Mbps-Gauge: 28 Gauge-Center Conductor: Tinned Copper -Connector Finish: Nickel -Shielding: Aluminum Foil and Braid-UL Rated: Yes-UL Rating: VW-1-Ferrite Cores: No-RoHS Compliant: Yes -Jacket Type: Xtra-Flex PVC-Jacket Color: Black -Warranty: Lifetime .The Pros understand that their systems are only as good as their cables. While they are far too smart to overpay for retail brands, the Pros also know a “bargain cable” that causes downtime is no bargain in the long run. Comprehensive cables have to work, every cable, every time so you can count on Comprehensive for a lifetime of worry- free performance.
